'''''Kwaku Ananse'''''  ni film ngufi ya 2013 iyobowe na Akosua Adoma Owusu . Filime ngufi ikomatanya ibintu byigice cya autobiographical hamwe numugani wa Kwaku Ananse, umunyamayeri mu nkuru zo muri [[Afrika]] yuburengerazuba na Karayibe bigaragara nkigitagangurirwa numugabo. Umugani wa Kwaku Ananse uhujwe ninkuru y'umusore wo hanze witwa Nyan Koronhwea, witabiriye gushyingura se. Mu gihe cyo gushyingura, yasubiye mu ishyamba ashakisha se. Iyi filime yakinnye n'umucuranzi w'icyamamare Koo Nimo n'umukinnyi w'amafirime w'inararibonye Grace Omaboe . 

Amashusho yanditswe hamwe n’umukinnyi wa firime wo muri Pakisitani n’umunyamerika akaba na rwiyemezamirimo Iram Parveen Bilal . Iyi nyandiko yandikiwe MaameYaa Boafo, umunyamerika wavukiye muri Pakisitani wavukiye muri [[Gana]], wahoze ari umukinnyi wa mbere nka Nyan Koronhwea. Ariko, itsinda ryababyaye mumujyi wa New York amaherezo ryafashe umwanzuro wo gusubiramo imico mugihe cyabanjirije umusaruro hamwe na Jojo Abot, umuhanzi ukomoka muri [[Gana]].  

== Inyandiko ==
Dushingiye ku migani ikungahaye yo muri [[Gana]], iyi filime ngufi y’ubumaji ihuza ibintu byanditswe mu buzima bwa Owusu n’imigenzo ya rubanda kugira ngo ivuga amateka y’umukobwa ukiri muto w’umunyamerika wagarutse muri [[Afurika]] y’iburengerazuba gushyingura se, ariko akavumbura umwirondoro we wihishe kabiri.

Kwaku Ananse ni umugani gakondo wo muri [[Afrika]] y'uburengerazuba kubyerekeye ikiremwa kigizwe numuntu nigitagangurirwa, kimara imyaka ikusanya ubwenge bwose bwisi mumasafuriya y'imbaho. Mugihe agerageza guhisha inkono mugiti, ntashobora kubona uburyo bwo kuyishyira hejuru mumashami yacyo. Iyo umuhungu we muto, Ntikuma amweretse inzira, Kwaku Ananse ararakara cyane, ajugunya inkono hasi. Iraturika kandi ubwenge burashira. Umuntu wese arihuta, yizeye gukiza ibyo ashoboye.

Nyan Koronhwea asubira kwa se Kwaku Ananse wavukiye muri [[Gana]] kumuhamba. Bari barabuze umubano hagati yabo kera. Yatandukanye ibyiyumvo by'ubuzima bwa se n'umuryango umwe muri [[Gana]] undi muri [[Amerika]]. Yarengewe n’ishyingurwa, asubira mu isi y’umwuka ashakisha Kwaku Ananse.  

== Ibihembo ==
''Kwaku Ananse'' yatorewe kuba Golden Bear mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Berlin kandi yegukana igihembo cyiza cya Filime ngufi mu bihembo bya 9 bya Afurika Movie Academy Academy Awards .    Iyi filime kandi yakiriye abacamanza badasanzwe mu Ishyirahamwe Cinémas et Cultures d'Afrique 2015 i Angers, mu Bufaransa.
